236
00:23:08,386 --> 00:23:10,972
Mereka melakukan pemotretan
untuk brosur humas sekarang.

237
00:23:11,306 --> 00:23:12,599
Bisakah kau ikut?

238
00:23:12,682 --> 00:23:14,101
Kurasa tidak.

239
00:23:14,184 --> 00:23:17,312
Ayolah!

240
00:23:17,521 --> 00:23:18,814
Hentikan!

241
00:23:18,897 --> 00:23:19,773
Ini dia.

242
00:23:19,856 --> 00:23:21,525
Jika sendirian,
dia tidak seperti detektif.

243
00:23:21,608 --> 00:23:23,777
Tentu saja tidak! Dia masih latihan.

244
00:23:24,152 --> 00:23:25,153
Ohyama!

245
00:23:25,237 --> 00:23:26,113
Ayo lakukan!

246
00:23:26,238 --> 00:23:27,864
Dia bawahanmu!

247
00:23:28,198 --> 00:23:29,116
Kau yang di kiri!

248
00:23:29,449 --> 00:23:30,992
Coba tampak lebih serius.

249
00:23:31,118 --> 00:23:33,328
Sakurai, coba tampak lebih percaya diri.

250
00:23:33,411 --> 00:23:34,412
- Baik.
- Siap?

251
00:23:34,871 --> 00:23:36,498
Baiklah.

252
00:23:37,249 --> 00:23:38,333
Kita mulai!

253
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:42,212
- Kenapa kau mau?
- Maaf.

254
00:23:42,420 --> 00:23:43,338
Mereka butuh wanita.

255
00:23:43,421 --> 00:23:44,506
Aku meragukannya.

256
00:23:44,589 --> 00:23:45,549
Sersan!

257
00:23:45,966 --> 00:23:47,217
Jangan terlalu cemberut.

258
00:23:47,509 --> 00:23:49,636
- Ayolah!
- Lakukan dengan benar!

259
00:23:49,719 --> 00:23:50,804
Berposelah!

260
00:23:50,887 --> 00:23:52,055
Baik, ayo coba lagi.

261
00:23:52,848 --> 00:23:53,890
Mulai.

262
00:23:55,433 --> 00:23:56,977
Bagus!

263
00:23:57,144 --> 00:23:58,103
Sekali lagi!

264
00:23:58,645 --> 00:24:00,355
Itu bagus!

265
00:24:00,522 --> 00:24:01,398
Sekali lagi!

266
00:24:01,982 --> 00:24:03,483
Bagus!

267
00:24:03,608 --> 00:24:04,484
Lagi!

268
00:24:04,776 --> 00:24:05,944
Bagus!

269
00:24:06,027 --> 00:24:07,696
Tampak bagus!

270
00:24:07,779 --> 00:24:08,947
Baiklah!

271
00:24:46,401 --> 00:24:48,528
Letnan Saegusa! Ini Ohyama!

272
00:24:48,653 --> 00:24:51,698
Aku di Rumah Sakit Memorial Tanihara
yang kau sebutkan!

273
00:24:54,201 --> 00:24:55,952
Perbincangan soal apa itu?

274
00:25:01,833 --> 00:25:03,585
Apakah aku sudah gila?

275
00:25:15,513 --> 00:25:17,015
Ohyama, itu kau?

276
00:25:19,935 --> 00:25:21,394
Ini Saegusa.

277
00:25:22,812 --> 00:25:24,731
Saegusa dari Polres Josai.

278
00:25:27,859 --> 00:25:29,027
Letnan...

279
00:25:31,696 --> 00:25:33,698
Syukurlah aku bisa menghubungimu.

280
00:25:35,909 --> 00:25:36,910
Begini...

281
00:25:38,995 --> 00:25:42,916
Bagaimana kau bisa tahu
tempat mayat Hashimoto berada?

282
00:25:44,876 --> 00:25:46,878
Bagaimana kau mengenalku?

283
00:25:49,506 --> 00:25:50,590
Ini mungkin

284
00:25:53,009 --> 00:25:55,262
kali terakhir kita bicara.

285
00:25:57,597 --> 00:25:59,849
Apa maksudmu?

286
00:26:01,726 --> 00:26:02,602
Namun,

287
00:26:05,397 --> 00:26:06,690
ini belum berakhir.

288
00:26:08,191 --> 00:26:09,276
Kau akan dihubungi lagi

289
00:26:11,111 --> 00:26:13,571
lewat radio.

290
00:26:15,949 --> 00:26:17,617
Yang akan menghubungimu

291
00:26:21,413 --> 00:26:22,664
adalah aku

292
00:26:24,582 --> 00:26:26,001
dari tiga tahun lalu.

293
00:26:26,918 --> 00:26:28,461
Sersan Ohyama

294
00:26:32,048 --> 00:26:33,133
dari

295
00:26:34,592 --> 00:26:36,553
tiga tahun lalu.

296
00:26:41,599 --> 00:26:44,019
Sersan, bicaramu tidak masuk akal.

297
00:26:45,603 --> 00:26:46,479
Masa lalu

298
